		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think a new replacement for Open tUME for multi-console use is useful, such features like:<br /><br />Plugins (to use any format)<br />Palette Editor<br />Nametable Editor<br />Map Editor<br />Sprite Editor<br />Graphics Editor<br />Import/Export<br />etc...<br /><br />This could be actually a useful revamp of a Project that Tepples is doing!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


